node.text:
Going to share this with you ‼️ It’s been a absolute awesome year for our YouTube channel “The Deegans”
 What started just having fun filming some videos on our phones that  turned into absolute cool  way to tell the family story our way. By the numbers it has become one of the most influential  dirtbike channels in existence. Thanks to you guys!! And I feel like we’re only getting started with the stories that are still yet to be told. A ton of work has gone into this many many hours of filming and editing. Special thanks to @gavenayala @ayalamedia and @buckywya our full time film guys that are part of the family always with us! (Putting up with the kids) It is a massive undertaking to put out five videos a week! Remember when we used to do one video a year? It is super satisfying seeing the results of so many people that consistently watch the channel and influences many to get into a healthy lifestyle  and the dirtbike world.  Like I said this has been a strong year for our channel as you can see the millions and millions of views  buy our audience that is absolutely global so many countries tune in !! Never thought there would be a system that would have such a global reach like this !!. Used to be Crusty Demons video once a year ha ha.! We r happy to see the almost billion hours watched  but make sure you take time to get out and ride your dirtbike!! Much love !! Now go out take some big risks and stay crazy!! #TheDeegans #dirtbike #moto #race #family #youtube  Link in bio to sub!  We are always open for cool ideas and colabs also ..
